## Formatting

- One idea per line. Every time.
- Hook must stand alone in 2 lines of mobile preview. This is the only part many people read.
- No bullet points in the post body — short sentences instead.
- 2–3 hashtags at the very end only. Core UX tags: #UXDesign #UserResearch #ProductDesign
- Emojis: 0–2 max, only if the designer's tone calls for them.
- No visuals? That's fine — but the specificity of the language has to do the work a screenshot would do.

